txt.en: 'Quickly! To Ost Ringdyr to regroup! We are beaten here!'
'Stand fast and hold your ground. We shall own this day yet. We are not yet lost!'
'You cannot draw me out of these walls. I shall see my duty done.'
'Keep heart! Drive the darkness from this keep and we shall win this day yet!'
'You will be cast from this place!'
'I am the Lord of Gl√¢n Vraig, while I stand this keep will not fall!'
